e Decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 14, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ammar ibn Yasir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for contentment with the decree of providence.\u201d Source: al-Sunnah li-Ibn Abi\u0304 \u2018A\u0304s\u0323im 128 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39766,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/ali-rida-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":39828,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Qadr: Acceptance of Allah\u2019s decree even if unpleasant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Agharr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, upon him be peace, saw \u2018Adi ibn Hatim in dismay. Ali said, \u201cO \u2018Adi, what is wrong that I see you sad and distressed?\u201d \u2018Adi said, \u201cWhy should I not be when my sons have been killed and my eye has been gouged?\u201d Ali\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height"